Create Learning Material
POST /api/learningmaterials
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "MaterialID": 1,
  "Type": "PDF",
  "Title": "Database Systems Lecture Notes",
  "URL": "https://example.com/db-notes.pdf",
  "StudentID": 5,
  "UploadedAt": "2025-09-09T14:30:00Z"
}

Get All Learning Materials
GET /api/learningmaterials

Get Learning Material by ID
GET /api/learningmaterials/1

Update Learning Material
PUT /api/learningmaterials/1
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "Type": "PDF",
  "Title": "Updated Database Systems Lecture Notes",
  "URL": "https://example.com/updated-db-notes.pdf"
}

Delete Learning Material
DELETE /api/learningmaterials/1